&lt;span class="profile-big-image-inner2"&gt; &lt;a href="/furusho"&gt;&lt;img class=" photo" src="/images/0001/5491/Furusho_Consegi_2009_640x480_big.jpg?1259196754" height="89" alt="Vitorio  Furusho" width="67"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="/furusho"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;Vitorio Furusho&lt;span class="long_text"&gt;&lt;span title="You can either do  that by getting involved in a local event organized by our teams  worldwide." style="background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;ODF Alliance Award&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.documentfreedom.org/Gubro-PR"&gt;&lt;br&gt;Gubro-PR&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Mar 2010 10:21:48 +0000</pubDate><link>http://softwarelivre.org/furusho/blog/dfd-2010-document-freedom-day-31-marco-participe-organize-e-realize-o-dfd-em-sua-instituicao-ou-localidade</link><guid>http://softwarelivre.org/furusho/blog/dfd-2010-document-freedom-day-31-marco-participe-organize-e-realize-o-dfd-em-sua-instituicao-ou-localidade</guid></item><item><title>Neelie Kroes da European Commissioner testemunha sobr padrão ODF</title><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="long_text"&gt;&lt;span title="“I know a smart business decision when I see  one — choosing open standards is a very smart business decision  indeed.” — Neelie Kroes, European Commissioner (Digital Agenda)  OpenForum Europe, Brussels, 10th June 2008" style="background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;"Eu sei que uma decisão  de negócio inteligente é quando vejo uma escolha de padrões abertos sendo uma  decisão empresarial de fato muito inteligente."&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
